<div class="c2">
<h2>COVID-19’s shock for emerging economies</h2>
<p class="intro">COVID-19 is by far the biggest challenge policymakers in emerging economies have had to deal with in recent history.
</p>
<div class="meta">
<span class="row"><span class="label">By: </span>The Sound of Economics</span>
